               <msContents>
                  <summary>Horologium for the Night Hours of Abba Giyorgis, Sä‘ätat, ሰዓታት: ዘአቡነ: ጊዮርጊስ: ዘሌሊት: , written in several different hands of the 18th and 19th centuries. The manuscript has been rebound in disorder.</summary>
